## âœ… Summary

| Term       | Meaning                                                |
| ---------- | ------------------------------------------------------ |
| TCP        | Transmission Control Protocol                          |
| Goal       | Deliver data **reliably** and **in order**             |
| Type       | **Connection-oriented** protocol                       |
| Importance | Backbone of **reliable communication** on the internet |

